        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill repeals the requirement for males between the ages of 18 and 26 to register with the Selective Service.</p> <p>The bill provides that an individual shall not be penalized for prior failure to register with the Selective Service. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
